<%= render "navbar" %>
<section class="proje">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="header text-center"><span>Galata</span></h1>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">
        <div class="proje-info">
          <p class="text p-skills"> Ruby | Ruby on Rails | Html | Css | Geocoder | JavaScript | Cloudinary | Heroku | PostgreSQL | Devise | Mapbox API | WebSockets | Figma</p>
          <p class="text">Galata is a mobile app built from scratch in a team of three in the final two weeks of the web development bootcamp at Le Wagon Istanbul in early 2021.</p>
           <p class="text">Galata is a tour guide for spontaneous travelers on a budget who are interested in enhancing their sightseeing experience.
            Users have access to content uploaded to the platform by other users such as articles, pictures, songs, podcasts and videos. On top of that,
             users can see other users who are close by on the map and have a conversation with them via a chat feature.</p>
          <div class="project-btn">
            <%= link_to "See Project", 'https://galata-b567.herokuapp.com/', target: 'blank', class: 'btn' %>
            <%= link_to "See Code", 'https://github.com/issamok3/galata', target: 'blank', class: 'btn' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-carousel">
          <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="3"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="4"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="5"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="6"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="7"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="8"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="9"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="10"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="11"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="12"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="13"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="14"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="15"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="16"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="17"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/root.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Galata allows travelers search sites near them with different options like filtering by category, address, and current location.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/filter.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/map.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Travelers can connect with other travelers via avatar on the map and can also easily access site content by clicking on a site marker.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/loader.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>When a user clicks the 'search by location' button, a rainbow loader activated by JavaScript runs untill the find current latitude and longitude of the User's location is calculated using Geocoder and show near users and sites on a Mapbox.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/index.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see sites near them with description and amount of the related contents.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/show.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can choose contents related to sites.</p>
                  <p> Audios, videos embedded from spotify and youtube and photos which is uploaded from Cloudinary and URLs are stored in the PostSQL database.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/contents.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Each of the contents icon made on Figma and used on website with  `svg` tag</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/videos.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see each of the embedded videos from youtube etc. and they can watch the video on the same page.</p>
                  <p>Users can like a piece of content and save it on to their Liked Content page.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/articles.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see each article with title and the avatar of the contributor. Each article is stored in the PostSQL database.</p>
                  <p>Users can like a piece of content and save it on to their Liked Content page.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/article.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/photos.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see site-related photos in a carousel.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/audios.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see each of the embedded audios from spotify and they can listen without leaving the page.</p>
                  <p>Users can like a piece of content and save it on to their Liked Content page.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/likedcontents.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see all pieces of content that they have liked.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/uploads.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>User can see their uploads and also upload new content about specific sites. Each uploads is stored in the PostSQL database.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/upload.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/settings.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Galata users can edit information.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/notifications.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Using WebSockets, a notification appears on top the user's avatar in the top right corner of the screen each time they get a new message.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/burger-navbar.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('galata/messages.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Using WebSockets, user can start a conversation with each other from the messages tab or from the user marker on the map.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
